<plot>Tim Mitchel, a high school student with the highest marks in his class, is attempting to run for student council vice president. Instead of studying up on his speech, he is catapulted into a blind date with a wild girl from the next town over. Tim begins to learn that things which he thought were a big deal in life were actually irrelevant in the grand scheme of things.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?508264</url></doc>
